
Ranger Help for: defend
=======================

SYNTAX:      defend <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   5
BASE SP:     20 sp
SKILL TYPE:  defensive

SUMMARY:    
This skill allows a Ranger to step in and defend a fellow explorer
from attack. There is a small chance that the creature that is fighting
your friend won't fall for your move and continue fighting them. Also,
you can't defend your enemy species.

